about.summary: An implementation of PEP 557: Data Classes

name: dataclasses
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.6" %}

package:
  name: dataclasses
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/d/dataclasses/dataclasses-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6988bd2b895eef432d562370bb707d540f32f7360ab13da45340101bc2307d84

build:
  number: 1
  skip: true  # [py==27]
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .  # [py==36]
  script: {{ PYTHON }} --version                                      # [py!=36]

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - dataclasses

about:
  home: https://github.com/ericvsmith/dataclasses
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: 'An implementation of PEP 557: Data Classes'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
